<h1>Your Story</h1>
<div style="width:80%;text-align:left;">
  <p>Please write a story about how you helped your client in a financial category and vehiicle. You can kepe the name anonymous. An example could be that I helped John Doe to get a life insurance to help with his retirement. In this case, the category is "retirement" and vehicle is "life insurance".</p>
  <p> A good story should include the following:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>What's your client's financial need?</li>
    <li>Why did you suggest the particular financial vehicle to your client?</li>
    <li>How did your service benefit and change the life of your client?</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Please note that your story won't be shown to the public until your profile is approved.</p> 
  <p> You may enter some partially completed story and come back to complete it after you submit this application.</p>
</div>
<%= form_for :broker, :url => setup_broker_path(@broker), :html => { :method => :put} do|f|%>
<table width="80%">
  <tr>
    <td>
      <%=f.select :financial_category, Order::FINANCIAL_CATEGORIES, {prompt:"Please Select Category"},{:class=>"form-control"}%>
    </td>
    <td>
      <%=f.select :product_id, Product.all.collect {|p| [ p.name, p.id ] }, {prompt:"Please Select Vehicle"},{:class=>"form-control"}%>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan=2>
      <%=f.text_area :story, {rows:"10", class:"form-control"}%>
    </td>
  </tr>
 
</table>
  <%=f.submit "Previous", name:"back", :class=>"btn btn-lg btn-default"%>
  <%=f.submit "Next",name:"next", :class=>"btn btn-lg btn-default"%>
<%end%>